4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Although not directly related to machine learning, the paper's focus on optimization problems may be of interest to researchers in the machine learning community. 
5. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with combinatorial optimization problems, which is a topic in discrete mathematics.
